: : Kup / Rodimus Prime : :

Kup turned to face Nightlight. He was about to answer her when Rodimus walked in, followed by Kenzo.

Kup: Are sensors have determined that it is a crystalized object, but nothing more. We are going to go investigate it. Nightlight, Kenzo, you two are welcome to come with us.

Rodimus Prime: Let&#39;s get going though, I want to know whats falling on our heads.

Prime and Kup walk out of the base. Once outside they transform to their respective alternate modes. The start to drive north into and hills. They drive slow waiting for Kenzo and Nightlight.
